&lt;li&gt;Project management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading initiatives and succeeding in a team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High-growth or early-stage startup experience is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge in the legal industry advantageous&lt;/li&gt;
